de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.index.tree.metrical.mtreevariants.mktrees.mktab

Class MkTabLeafEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.index.tree.AbstractLeafEntry
      • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.index.tree.metrical.mtreevariants.MTreeLeafEntry
        • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.index.tree.metrical.mtreevariants.mktrees.mktab.MkTabLeafEntry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Entry, LeafEntry, MkTabEntry, MTreeEntry, Externalizable, Serializable

     class MkTabLeafEntry
extends MTreeLeafEntry
implements MkTabEntry
    Represents an entry in a leaf node of a MkTab-Tree. Additionally to a MTreeLeafEntry a MkTabLeafEntry holds a list of its knn distances for parameters k <= k_max.
    Since:
    0.2
    Author:
    Elke Achtert
